Just stay focused on the case.

18:00.800 --> 18:03.280
Yes. I will.

18:03.440 --> 18:10.280
Excuse me... I'll be focused...
I have to take this.

18:10.440 --> 18:12.560
This is Cecilie.

18:17.240 --> 18:21.480
